item.description:
Let's try Karaoke at a new venue in Saugus.

This is a non-exclusive event which means that we will be mixing in with the venue's regular patrons. The good news: No fee for attending. The bad news: longer waits for your turn at the microphone.

We can sit together as a group or we can mingle with everybody else. In fact, you don't need to sign up for this meetup; you can just show up.

I'm sorry for the late notice! Thanks go out to Cathy for suggesting the venue.
